Task
Write a Go-program that listens on port 8080 for a PUT request with a body containing an array of Integers in a JSON
format, and converts them to a string -> integer map that holds odd and even number separately in sorted slices. The result
shall be returned in the body of the response as text.

Create an issue for yourself
Create a new branch in the format #-<ISSUE_NAME>
Create a user specific directory in the pkg/learn-go directory
Implement the solution including tests in that directory
Test your solution by running go test ./...
File a pull request (PR), review someone elseâ€™s PR, and wait for someone to review your PR
Merge the PR to main & Close the issue